flowRoot.flowPara: Contents pane - a list of all the layers in a map. Acts as a key.
Map panel - shows current view of layers and location
Tabs for panes, e.g. Catalog, Search, Geoprocessing. (These may also appear on right-hand side of window)
Coordinates at the location of the tip of mouse pointer on map
Tooltips display when mouse pointer hovers over an item on a toolbar
Note that items may appear in different places on different computers.
Layer name - tick shows that it's visible on the map
Current scale of map - change scale using the dropdown.
"Ribbon" - quick access to key tools and commands. Changes with context.
